'''南蘇丹共和國'''（{{lang-en|Republic of South Sudan}}），通稱'''南蘇丹'''（{{lang-en|South Sudan}}），是[[非洲|非洲]]東北部一個[[內陸國家|內陸國家]]，2011年從[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]獨立。東面是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]，南面是[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]、[[肯亞|肯亞]]和[[烏干達|烏干達]]，西面是[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]，北面是[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]。包含[[白尼羅河|白尼羅河]]所形成廣闊的[[蘇德沼澤|蘇德沼澤]]。目前首都是第一大城市[[朱巴|朱巴]]，未來計畫將遷都到位置較居中的[[拉姆塞爾|拉姆塞爾]]。現代南蘇丹與蘇丹共和國的領土原為[[埃及|埃及]]的[[穆罕默德·阿里王朝|穆罕默德·阿里王朝]]佔據，後來成為[[英埃共管蘇丹|英埃共管蘇丹]]，1956年[[蘇丹共和國|蘇丹共和國]]獨立後成為其一部分，被劃分為南部10省。[[第一次蘇丹內戰|第一次蘇丹內戰]]後，蘇丹南方於1972年至1983年得到自治。[[第二次蘇丹內戰|第二次蘇丹內戰]]於1983年爆發，至2005年簽署《全面和平條約》，成立[[南蘇丹歷史|蘇丹南方自治政府]]。2011年，[[南蘇丹獨立公投|南蘇丹獨立公投]]以98.83%通過，南蘇丹共和國於2011年7月9日0时宣告獨立，有30个國家的[[國家元首|國家元首]]或政府代表参加南苏丹共和国的独立庆典仪式，[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]也参加了成立仪式。2011年7月14日南苏丹共和国正式加入[[聯合國|聯合國]]成为聯合國[[聯合國會員國|会员国]]。目前也為[[非洲聯盟|非洲聯盟]]、[[東非共同體|東非共同體]]等組織的成員國。2012年7月，簽署了[[日內瓦公約|日內瓦公約]]。南蘇丹獨立之後仍然有激烈的內部衝突，2014年以後在[[失败国家指数|脆弱國家指數]]（前身為失敗國家指數）的評分一直是全球最高。有分析指出，南苏丹独立后遭受了种族暴力，并经历了[[南苏丹内战|内战]]，其特点是[[南苏丹人权|侵犯人权]]，包括各种种族屠杀和冲突各方在2013年至2020年2月22日期间杀害记者且当时相互竞争和战斗的领导人[[萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特|萨尔瓦·基尔·马亚尔迪特]]和[[里克·马查尔|里克·马查尔]]达成了团结协议，组建了[[联合政府|联合政府]]，<ref name="power-sharing">{{cite news |title=South Sudan rivals strike power-sharing deal |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-51562367 |access-date=28 February 2020 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=22 February 2020 |archive-date=2020-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226015108/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-51562367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>为难民回国铺平了道路。<ref name=malak>{{cite web | last=Malak | first=Garang A. | title=Trust issues persist in Juba despite new dawn | website=The East African | date=22 February 2020 | url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/ea/Trust-issues-persist-in-South-Sudan/4552908-5464954-format-xhtml-fexisgz/index.html | access-date=20 June 2020 | archive-date=2020-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622081027/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/news/ea/Trust-issues-persist-in-South-Sudan/4552908-5464954-format-xhtml-fexisgz/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

南苏丹人口主要由[[尼格罗人|尼格罗人]]组成，在人口统计上属于世界上最年轻的国家，大约有一半不到18岁。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2018/09/1018671|title='Children's crisis' in South Sudan must be addressed, says top UN official calling for real accountability|date=7 September 2018|access-date=30 September 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930193622/https://news.un.org/en/story/2018/09/1018671|archive-date=30 September 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>大多数居民信奉[[基督教|基督教]]或各种[[非洲传统宗教|土著信仰]]。该国是[[联合国会员国|联合国会员国]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-sudan-un-membership-idUKTRE76D3I120110714 |title=South Sudan admitted to U.N. as 193rd member |last=Worsnip |first=Patrick |date=14 July 2011 |work=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |access-date=24 July 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715144119/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/07/14/uk-sudan-un-membership-idUKTRE76D3I120110714 |archive-date=15 July 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=39034&Cr=South+Sudan&Cr1= |title=UN welcomes South Sudan as 193rd Member State |publisher=United Nations News Service |date=14 July 2011 |access-date=14 July 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803100613/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=39034&Cr=South+Sudan&Cr1= |archive-date=3 August 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>、[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]<ref name="au54">{{cite web |url=http://www.voanews.com/english/news/africa/east/South-Sudan-Becomes-African-Unions-54th-Member-126320433.html |title=South Sudan Becomes African Union's 54th Member |publisher=Voice of America News |date=28 July 2011 |access-date=28 July 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916115846/http://www.voanews.com/english/news/africa/east/South-Sudan-Becomes-African-Unions-54th-Member-126320433.html |archive-date=16 September 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>、[[东非共同体|东非共同体]]、政府间发展管理局<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-11-25/ethiopia-agrees-to-back-somalia-army-operations-igad-says.html |title=Ethiopia Agrees to Back Somalia Army Operations, IGAD Says |agency=Bloomberg Businessweek |access-date=25 November 2011 |date=25 November 2011 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120729154359/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-11-25/ethiopia-agrees-to-back-somalia-army-operations-igad-says.html |archive-date=29 July 2012 }}</ref>并且是[[日内瓦公约|日内瓦公约]]的缔约国。<ref name="South Sudan Signs Geneva Conventions">{{cite web |url=http://www.freedomhouse.org/article/freedom-house-congratulates-south-sudan-signing-geneva-conventions |title=Freedom House Congratulates South Sudan for Signing the Geneva Conventions |date=20 July 2012 |publisher=Freedom House |access-date=20 July 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721023635/http://www.freedomhouse.org/article/freedom-house-congratulates-south-sudan-signing-geneva-conventions |archive-date=21 July 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref>截至2019年，南苏丹在最新的联合国[[世界幸福报告|世界幸福报告]]中排名倒数第三，<ref>{{cite web|title=World Happiness Report 2018|url=http://worldhappiness.report/ed/2018/|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213084642/http://worldhappiness.report/ed/2018/|archive-date=13 December 2018|access-date=4 December 2018|publisher=World Happiness Report|page=23}}</ref>在[[全球和平指数|全球和平指数]]上排名倒數第三，在美国和平基金[[脆弱国家指数|脆弱国家指数]]上排名第四。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://fragilestatesindex.org/data/|title=Fragile States Index|publisher=Fund for Peace|access-date=4 December 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715052132/https://fragilestatesindex.org/data/|archive-date=15 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
